<h1>Your Question is Ready</h1>

<div class="para">The link to share for expressing preferences is:</div>
<div>
<a class="displayLink" href="<%= choice_path %>">Click here to see your
question.  Copy this link to share!</a>
</div>
<div>Share the link with others by post or email.  Most browsers will allow
you to right click on the link and copy to your clipboard.  Then you can
paste the link to an email, blog entry, or web entry.</div>

<div class="para">The link for viewing the result will be:</div>
<div>
<a class="displayLink" href="<%= result_choice_path %>">View result of
question, <%= @choice.title %></a>
</div>

<div class="para">To edit your choice before anyone has expressed a preference, go
to:</div>
<div>
<a class="displayLink" href="<%= edit_choice_path %>">Click here to edit
your question,
<%= @choice.title %></a>
</div>

<%= render :partial => 'display', :object => @choice %>

<%= button_to 'Socelect home', root_path %>
